{{Infobox medical person |name = Alexandre Okinczyc |box_width = |image = Alexandre okinczyc.jpeg |image_width = |alt = |caption = |birth_date = 28 January 1839 |birth_place = [[Sialiec, Biaroza raion|Sielec]], [[Grodno Governorate]], [[Russian Empire]] (now [[Belarus]]) |death_date = 18 March 1886 |death_place = [[Villepreux]], [[Third French Republic|France]] |profession = "Médecin des pauvres" |specialism = |research_field = |known_for = |years_active = |education = |work_institutions = |prizes = |relations = |signature = }}
'''Alexandre Okinczyc''' ({{lang-be|Аляксандар Акінчыц}}, '''Aliaksandr Akinchyts''', 1839–1886)<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://ensmp.net/literacy/okinczyc.html |title=Alexandre Okinczyc (1839–1886) |access-date=2009-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100823003904/http://ensmp.net/literacy/okinczyc.html |archive-date=2010-08-23 |dead-url=yes |df= }}</ref> was a Polish and French 19th century physician and memoirist of [[Belarusians|Belarusian]] ethnicity.
He sent to [[Siberia]] by [[Alexander II of Russia|Tsar Alexander II's]] troops after participating in the [[January Uprising]] in [[Belarus]], [[Poland]] and [[Lithuania]]. From there he succeeded to escape to the West. He established in [[France]] and became a known [[physician|doctor]].
There he wrote in [[Polish language|Polish]] the story of his adventure, which was later translated to [[French language|French]] by Joséphine Bohdan. The original Polish written version of the memoirs seems to be owned by Jean and Madeleine Okinczyc.<ref>[http://pages.interlog.com/~mineykok/Okin1.html Memoires by Doctor Alexander Okinczyc] translated by Krzysztof Mineyko</ref> The doctor died in [[Villepreux]]. There, the "Association des amis du vieux Villepreux" offers a [[museum]] about the "Docteur Alexandre" and there is a street named "rue du Docteur Alexandre".<ref>[https://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&source=s_q&hl=en&geocode=&q=rue+du+docteur+alexandre,+villepreux&sll=37.0625,-95.677068&sspn=36.368578,79.013672&ie=UTF8&hq=&hnear=Rue+du+Docteur+Alexandre,+78450+Villepreux,+Yvelines,+Ile-de-France,+France&ll=48.835007,2.011614&spn=0.007387,0.01929&z=16&iwloc=A rue du Docteur Alexandre]</ref>
