'''Bleikvatnet''' is a [[lake]] in the municipality of [[Hemnes]] in [[Nordland]] county, [[Norway]]. The lake lies about {{convert|5|km}} northeast of the village of [[Bleikvasslia]]. The {{convert|12.59|km2|adj=on}} lake is regulated by a [[dam]]. The water flows out to the south and then down a {{convert|64|m|adj=on}} tall [[waterfall]] on the river Bleikvasselva.<ref name="snl">{{cite web|url=http://snl.no/Bleikvasselva|title=Bleikvasselva|author=Store norske leksikon|authorlink=Store norske leksikon|language=Norwegian|accessdate=2011-12-05}}</ref>
