Dr '''Helen S. King''' was a South African oncologist{{sfn|Mills|2013|p=245}} and anti-apartheid campaigner.{{sfn|Horrell|1973|p=393}}<ref name="poli_Cape" />  She was married to [[Edward King (priest)|Edward King]], former 
[[Dean (religion)|Dean]] of [[St. George's Cathedral, Cape Town|Cape Town]].  She was awarded the [[Order of Simon of Cyrene]] in 1996.  King died in 2015.

